                                                                    "value": "Before deciding which university to transfer to, it is important to research the minimum entry requirements for the transfer program, application deadlines, and international college credit transfer policies. International college credit transfer policies help you understand the minimum amount of credits you need to have completed at your current university to be eligible to transfer, and how many credits can be transferred to the university you have selected.",
