                                                                    "nodeType": "text",
                                                                    "value": "Coordinate with both your current advisor and the advisor of the university you are transferring to for requesting and submitting all required documentation. Usually, this involves the same documents you provided to your current university, such as your academic records, letter of recommendation, and standardized test scores. Depending on the program you are enrolling in, you may also be required to take additional tests or certifications before being admitted. Be sure to clarify all requirements with an advisor!",
