                                                {
                                                    "data": {},
                                                    "marks": [],
                                                    "value": "From cars and computers to skyscrapers and solar energy, engineers develop, build, and improve our everyday lives. A degree in engineering from one of our partner universities will help you develop your technical skillset in math, science, and problem solving.",
                                                    "nodeType": "text"
                                                }
