                                                                "nodeType": "text",
                                                                "value": "Most master’s in economics at US universities do not require you to have majored in economics during your undergraduate degree — though these requirements may be different for each university. Many of these programs allow you to enroll with a bachelor’s from any discipline. ",
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "data": {}
