                                            "name": "How Many Years Does it Take to Earn a Master of Finance Degree in the US?",
                                            "question": {
                                                "nodeType": "document",
                                                "data": {},
                                                "content": [
                                                    {
                                                        "nodeType": "paragraph",
                                                        "content": [
                                                            {
                                                                "nodeType": "text",
                                                                "value": "How many years does it take to earn a master of finance degree in the US?",
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "data": {}
                                                            }
                                                        ],
                                                        "data": {}
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            "answer": {
                                                "data": {},
                                                "content": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {},
                                                        "content": [
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {},
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "value": "Typically, it takes one to two years to complete a master’s in finance USA. This duration can change depending on different universities, as some universities offer accelerator programs that let you complete your degree in one year or less. Some programs are also available online over a shorter duration, and can allow you to start your degree from your home country before you complete it in the US. ",
                                                                "nodeType": "text"
                                                            }
                                                        ],
                                                        "nodeType": "paragraph"
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {},
                                                        "content": [
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {},
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "value": "The duration of your finance graduate program can also change because of your academic performance, the types of coursework you have selected, the number of semesters you are enrolled, and if the program has a thesis component. Additionally, studying your MS in finance in USA universities part time can extend the duration of your degree by up to five years, depending on your course schedule. Your degree may also take longer if you are pursuing another master’s from a different field as part of a ",
                                                                "nodeType": "text"
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {
                                                                    "uri": "https://www.shorelight.com/student-stories/dual-degree-programs-vs-double-majors-how-to-choose/"
                                                                },
                                                                "content": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "data": {},
                                                                        "marks": [],
                                                                        "value": "dual degree",
                                                                        "nodeType": "text"
                                                                    }
                                                                ],
                                                                "nodeType": "hyperlink"
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {},
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "value": ". Participating in an internship during your degree may also extend the duration depending on the type of work you do. ",
                                                                "nodeType": "text"
                                                            }
                                                        ],
                                                        "nodeType": "paragraph"
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {},
                                                        "content": [
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {},
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "value": "Additionally, if you need to complete certain courses as part of your master’s in finance requirements USA, your masters may take slightly longer to complete. You can avoid these prerequisite courses if you have a ",
                                                                "nodeType": "text"
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {
                                                                    "uri": "https://shorelight.com/universities/undergraduate/international/finance/"
                                                                },
                                                                "content": [
                                                                    {
                                                                        "data": {},
                                                                        "marks": [],
                                                                        "value": "bachelor’s degree in finance",
                                                                        "nodeType": "text"
                                                                    }
                                                                ],
                                                                "nodeType": "hyperlink"
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {},
                                                                "marks": [],
                                                                "value": ", which usually takes four years to complete. While not always a requirement, a bachelor’s in finance equips you with the fundamentals you need to understand the topics you will be studying in a graduate program. ",
                                                                "nodeType": "text"
                                                            }
                                                        ],
                                                        "nodeType": "paragraph"
                                                    }
                                                ],
                                                "nodeType": "document"
                                            }
