                                                                "value": " by helping you learn advanced management concepts and skills used in modern-day financial markets. While a bachelor of finance would teach you the basics, a graduate program in finance helps you understand analytical techniques and teaches you about cutting-edge financial technology (also known as fintech). ",
                                                                "nodeType": "text"
