                                                                "nodeType": "text",
                                                                "value": "Unlike the course curriculum for bachelor’s degree programs in computer science, the course curriculum for computer science master’s USA may offer multiple specializations. Depending on your goals and interests, as well as advice from your advisors, you can build your own curriculum. However, this may vary depending on the US university you wish to attend and your specialization.",
